see this city, Hanoi,

02:42.245 --> 02:45.373
than from a motorbike
or a scooter.

02:45.415 --> 02:49.003
To do otherwise would
be to miss it all.

02:52.631 --> 02:55.216
♪

02:55.258 --> 02:56.802
